Savant Application Framework v0.something (the current development branch is managed by github: git@github.com:Broncko/Savant.git)

Welcome!

Following a few things to get started with Savant. You can find the complete documentation in docs/Documentation (e.g. docs/Documentation/html/en/Savant.docbook.html).

in a nutshell:
1. set up a virtual host on your webserver which points to the Savant/htdocs directory.
2. set the correct file permissions (there will be a script for that shortly)
3. call the url leading to the url from a webbrowser
